{"tid":1391300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 如何提高夢中裝備使用效率","createTime":"2019-07-31T11:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T13:08:55.000Z","uid":243262,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"887cd811844e7b5a93f01aa90f778cd89f7a5322","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"自從出左post話有義士為左買裝備搞到唔夠錢食飯後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信大家呢幾日都好努力咁四出網羅物資<br />\n有望係黎緊星期六既旺角仲有星期日既西區/將軍澳提供到一批新既裝備出黎<br />\n<br />\n但係增加物資供應既同時，我地係咪都應該減少物資既浪費？<br />\n我既諗法係，義士們撤退時為左減少風險而放棄裝備係無可奈何既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁架話會唔會可以有一班人可以係義士既撤退路線上standby，幫佢地回收裝備？<br />\n比如係地鐵站或車箱內，遊下地鐵河<br />\n交到各車站做緊哨兵同接放學既爸爸媽媽拎走？<br />\n再大膽d既，係狗收隊後，回到戰區收集返路邊既裝備？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外口罩既濾罐、濾棉都有官方既使用次數限制<br />\n (物資供應隨時不足甚至被中斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，供目前不建議定下次用次數上限)<br />\n對於被回收既裝備，同埋義士們依家手頭上既裝備<br />\n平日除左搵密實袋保存之餘 (加埋吸濕大苯象會唔會好d？)<br />\n會唔會可以搵marker畫一畫佢，寫上第一次使用日期<br />\n而每一次使用後都畫返一條線上去<br />\n咁架話就可以方便義士們將較新既裝備交比前線，特別係滅煙隊使用。<br />\n<br />\n咁架話義士係前線發現裝備有失效之嫌時<br />\n亦較易判定出原因係咪來自裝備的老化<br />\n定係自己使用不當戴得唔好/狗又用過期野or加料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n確定為老化後亦可以整爛個濾罐或者用marker油花晒佢<br />\n<br />\n好鬼死長,sorry for 1999<br />\n希望大家可以一齊研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ff0bdeefa2ba8662fa7c9baa1a659a14afc4c6","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28755b390e4f6c3285d96b77cf4957741dc1ba00","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d9f4dbfa62c2a1970392a5bbbd840afbb2362be","tid":1391300,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:37:17.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"0bb71083e0b188aeb4bb003455a06c757cab6424","tid":1391300,"uid":218923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:37:43.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"59c2ea4aa476bd063068bddb2ef2ef6f658e175a","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65838ce68d6f697311d3fb399a131f43737ccd49","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:43:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53bdfa368753607b1edd4bddd1a00419564aa9c9","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf3d344dfb5acb80a50910a6afa263d00499b013","tid":1391300,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【暗黑經濟學】發夢原則<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390973</a><br />\n在資源有限和時間性下，必須建築一件大夢，我們夢醒之時，敵人就再無夢可發。現在，我們要先改變造夢思維。<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"ec3d061ab6ac32c9a5afd6652f36ea862a716e15","tid":1391300,"uid":202889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"其實係清場後 住附近嘅落樓執得唔得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8a152e652aade277e2ba0658567f0901cc5fa4","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa67e6e0c4099b69955f18ab6fae2c32047b7322","tid":1391300,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"一齊研究執物資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成立拾荒小隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85adb6f245db0562c1c8d7d4ae0aab1736a2976","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec3d061ab6ac32c9a5afd6652f36ea862a716e15","tid":1391300,"uid":202889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"其實係清場後 住附近嘅落樓執得唔得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"要諗辦法令和理非都大膽d"},{"pid":"fd6dfb9ef575ec89d224bea9ba580c57f779a87c","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"097e1fe727d0bc024b163d30409e90cb89884905","tid":1391300,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:46:31.000Z","msg":"其實住非高危地區，返歸途中係冇掉裝既必要<br />\n<br />\n唔好再盲目掉裝，多多都唔夠洗呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其係預視到黎緊會有好多s級神裝送到，呢堆野掉左就真係短時間內買唔返架喇"},{"pid":"18cb3af48b64c370f000825a917b011b0cd9cfaf","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"097e1fe727d0bc024b163d30409e90cb89884905","tid":1391300,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:46:31.000Z","msg":"其實住非高危地區，返歸途中係冇掉裝既必要<br />\n<br />\n唔好再盲目掉裝，多多都唔夠洗呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其係預視到黎緊會有好多s級神裝送到，呢堆野掉左就真係短時間內買唔返架喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:59:22.000Z","msg":"但前線返屋企時又真係好驚既<br />\n最好都係搵人幫佢地收左d裝？"},{"pid":"152f15bdc47660322dc82af39b0a7ef2919016a5","tid":1391300,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18cb3af48b64c370f000825a917b011b0cd9cfaf","tid":1391300,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"097e1fe727d0bc024b163d30409e90cb89884905","tid":1391300,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:46:31.000Z","msg":"其實住非高危地區，返歸途中係冇掉裝既必要<br />\n<br />\n唔好再盲目掉裝，多多都唔夠洗呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其係預視到黎緊會有好多s級神裝送到，呢堆野掉左就真係短時間內買唔返架喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:59:22.000Z","msg":"但前線返屋企時又真係好驚既<br />\n最好都係搵人幫佢地收左d裝？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:08:55.000Z","msg":"如果可以搵到人收就最好啦<br />\n<br />\n如果搵唔到人收既希望真係盡量可以keep返自己一套<br />\n眼罩口罩呢堆野拎出街係合法既<br />\n狗要咬你，你個袋裝支水都係武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且款式差唔多個個一樣，其實係冇可能用呢堆眼罩豬嘴去認得出你<br />\n<br />\n最前線真正令到你有危機既係你發夢時既所有衣著，尤其係d有花紋/特別掛飾既衫褲鞋袋<br />\n要掉就真係首要掉左d認到你既衣物先"}]}